#: ../../source/contributing.md:1
msgid "Contributing to IR-SIM"
msgstr "为 IR-SIM 做贡献"

#: ../../source/contributing.md:3
msgid ""
"Thank you for your interest in improving IR-SIM! Whether you're fixing a "
"typo, adding a new feature, or writing documentation, your contribution is "
"welcome by opening an issue or a pull request to the `main` branch. Below "
"are a few guidelines to help you get started."
msgstr ""
"感谢您对改进 IR-SIM 的关注！无论是修复拼写错误、添加新功能还是编写文档，我们都欢迎您通过向 `main` 分支提交 issue 或 pull "
"request 来贡献。以下是一些帮助您入门的指南。"

#: ../../source/contributing.md:5
#, python-format
msgid ""
"New here? Browse issues labelled **[good first "
"issue](https://github.com/hanruihua/ir-"
"sim/issues?q=is%3Aissue+is%3Aopen+label%3A%22good+first+issue%22)** for a "
"friendly starting point. By participating, you agree to uphold our **[Code "
"of Conduct](https://github.com/hanruihua/ir-"
"sim/blob/main/CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md)**."
msgstr ""
"新来的朋友？可以浏览带有 **[good first issue](https://github.com/hanruihua/ir-"
"sim/issues?q=is%3Aissue+is%3Aopen+label%3A%22good+first+issue%22)** 标签的 "
"issue，作为友好的起点。参与本项目即表示你同意遵守我们的 **[行为准则](https://github.com/hanruihua/ir-"
"sim/blob/main/CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md)**。"

#: ../../source/contributing.md:9
msgid "What You Can Contribute"
msgstr "您可以贡献什么"

#: ../../source/contributing.md:11
msgid "**Source Code**"
msgstr "**源代码**"

#: ../../source/contributing.md:12
msgid "New features (sensors, controllers, kinematic models)"
msgstr "新功能（传感器、控制器、运动学模型）"

#: ../../source/contributing.md:13
msgid "Bug fixes and performance improvements"
msgstr "错误修复和性能改进"

#: ../../source/contributing.md:15
msgid "**Documentation**"
msgstr "**文档**"

#: ../../source/contributing.md:16
msgid "Fix typos, clarify API descriptions"
msgstr "修复拼写错误，完善 API 描述"

#: ../../source/contributing.md:17
msgid "Add new tutorials or usage guides"
msgstr "添加新的教程或使用指南"

#: ../../source/contributing.md:18
msgid ""
"Improve examples under [`docs/`](https://ir-sim.readthedocs.io/en/stable/)"
msgstr "改进 [`docs/`](https://ir-sim.readthedocs.io/en/stable/) 下的示例"

#: ../../source/contributing.md:20
msgid "**Usage Examples & Tests**"
msgstr "**使用示例与测试**"

#: ../../source/contributing.md:21
msgid ""
"Extend or polish the [`usage/`](https://github.com/hanruihua/ir-"
"sim/tree/main/usage) directory"
msgstr ""
"扩展或完善 [`usage/`](https://github.com/hanruihua/ir-sim/tree/main/usage) 目录"

#: ../../source/contributing.md:22
msgid "Add unit tests for new features"
msgstr "为新功能添加单元测试"

#: ../../source/contributing.md:24
msgid "**Discussion & Design**"
msgstr "**讨论与设计**"

#: ../../source/contributing.md:25
msgid "Propose architectural changes"
msgstr "提出架构变更建议"

#: ../../source/contributing.md:26
msgid "Provide feedback on roadmap or UX"
msgstr "对路线图或用户体验提供反馈"

#: ../../source/contributing.md:30
msgid "Code Style"
msgstr "代码风格"

#: ../../source/contributing.md:32
msgid ""
"We use **[Ruff](https://docs.astral.sh/ruff/)** to format and lint Python "
"code. Before opening a PR, run:"
msgstr ""
"我们使用 **[Ruff](https://docs.astral.sh/ruff/)** 来格式化和检查 Python 代码。在提交 PR "
"之前，请运行："

#: ../../source/contributing.md:39
msgid ""
"To enable automatic checks on each commit, install the pre-commit hook:"
msgstr "要在每次提交时启用自动检查，请安装 pre-commit 钩子："

#: ../../source/contributing.md:48
msgid "Documentation"
msgstr "文档"

#: ../../source/contributing.md:50
msgid ""
"IR-SIM's documentation lives in the `docs/` directory and uses the [PyData "
"Sphinx Theme](https://pydata-sphinx-theme.readthedocs.io/en/stable/). To "
"build the docs locally:"
msgstr ""
"IR-SIM 的文档位于 `docs/` 目录，使用 [PyData Sphinx Theme](https://pydata-sphinx-"
"theme.readthedocs.io/en/stable/)。要在本地构建文档："

#: ../../source/contributing.md:57
msgid "New tutorials or guides belong in `docs/` or under `usage/`"
msgstr "新的教程或指南应放在 `docs/` 或 `usage/` 目录下"

#: ../../source/contributing.md:58
msgid "The API reference is auto-generated from docstrings"
msgstr "API 参考文档由 docstring 自动生成"

#: ../../source/contributing.md:62
msgid "Adding New Features"
msgstr "添加新功能"

#: ../../source/contributing.md:64
msgid ""
"Current support of sensors, behaviors, and robot kinematics models can be "
"seen in the [support](https://github.com/hanruihua/ir-sim?tab=readme-ov-"
"file#support)."
msgstr ""
"当前支持的传感器、行为和机器人运动学模型可在 [support](https://github.com/hanruihua/ir-"
"sim?tab=readme-ov-file#support) 中查看。"

#: ../../source/contributing.md:66
msgid ""
"New features to support more platforms and scenarios to make IR-SIM more "
"versatile are welcome. Please open an issue to discuss the design. If you "
"prefer, you can also email `hanrh@connect.hku.hk` for a design discussion."
msgstr ""
"欢迎添加新功能以支持更多平台和场景，使 IR-SIM 更加通用。请提交 issue 讨论设计方案。如果您愿意，也可以发送邮件至 "
"`hanrh@connect.hku.hk` 进行设计讨论。"

#: ../../source/contributing.md:70
msgid "Testing"
msgstr "测试"

#: ../../source/contributing.md:72
msgid "We use **pytest** for our test suite. To run all tests:"
msgstr "我们使用 **pytest** 作为测试框架。要运行所有测试："

#: ../../source/contributing.md:78
msgid "Please add tests for any new functionality or bug fix."
msgstr "请为任何新功能或错误修复添加测试。"

#: ../../source/contributing.md:82
msgid "Pull Requests"
msgstr "Pull Request"

#: ../../source/contributing.md:84
msgid ""
"Open pull requests against the `main` branch, and keep each PR focused on a "
"single change. Before submitting, run `ruff check` and `pytest`."
msgstr ""
"请向 `main` 分支提交 pull request，并让每个 PR 聚焦于单一改动。提交前请运行 `ruff check` 与 `pytest`。"

#: ../../source/contributing.md:86
msgid ""
"Use a [Conventional Commits](https://www.conventionalcommits.org/)-style "
"title — `<type>(<scope>): <subject>` — where `<type>` is one of `feat`, "
"`fix`, `docs`, `style`, `refactor`, `test`, or `chore` (the scope is "
"optional):"
msgstr ""
"请使用 [Conventional Commits](https://www.conventionalcommits.org/) 风格的标题 —— "
"`<type>(<scope>): <subject>` —— 其中 `<type>` 为 "
"`feat`、`fix`、`docs`、`style`、`refactor`、`test` 或 `chore` 之一（scope 可选）："

#: ../../source/contributing.md:96
msgid "Thanks again for helping make IR-SIM better!"
msgstr "再次感谢您帮助改进 IR-SIM！"
